n試過驚到忍住幾日唔痾， 一番到屋企一次過痾左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常都驚醫院 唔係打針就開刀 <br />\n點都要痛<br />\n比你講到我好想入去攬到大貓訓 唔鳩理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咁誇<br />\n人地bb 仔都好需要你錫架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大貓已經係大人，可以獨當一面架啦"},{"pid":"5e4b21948dc11d9dbfa718fbb4773dd6f9d58a5c","tid":88752,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係岩岩加貓<br />\n頭幾日真係要好忍心困住佢先<br />\n點嗌都唔好理，你唔好發岀任何聲音</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地就好<br />\n咁多貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a636a871e9966e453ba54082bde6465152bb40","tid":88752,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:40:21.000Z","msg":"更新 我岩岩播緊史上最好聽（youtube話）嘅大悲咒比佢聽<br />\n佢淨左兩分鐘 （恰著左）就繼續嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d62f2d3801615f402ed87af2cadc9cbd478d973","tid":88752,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更新 我岩岩播緊史上最好聽（youtube話）嘅大悲咒比佢聽<br />\n佢靜左兩分鐘 （恰著左）就繼續嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇播嘅原因係電話冇電熄左（電話都攰）"},{"pid":"93dba38ee8d787560ef8cea24586d3ef87667ede","tid":88752,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咁誇<br />\n人地bb 仔都好需要你錫架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大貓已經係大人，可以獨當一面架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢永遠都係我粒小bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢冇野係唔驚 人 狗 任何貓<br />\n有陌生人黎我屋企 佢會驚到匿埋房個櫃頂最入<br />\n去睇獸醫覆診 隔黎有隻大狗吠左野 佢驚到縮埋一舊狂震<br />\n去到人地啲幾隻貓嘅屋企 不論啲貓大過佢定細過佢 <br />\n佢都想同啲貓做朋友 然後比其他貓鬧 再面懞懞咁走"},{"pid":"eea3367c17a26a7e0834f014fdbe4be863691216","tid":88752,"uid":7517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更新 我岩岩播緊史上最好聽（youtube話）嘅大悲咒比佢聽<br />\n佢淨左兩分鐘 （恰著左）就繼續嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a9227c65a35456539d117e95a808f200e4bafa","tid":88752,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:54:26.000Z","msg":"貓B一定係咁 當初我接我細女返黎都係<br />\n叫到我都好怕佢會啞 係幾日後就唔再嘈<br />\n你大貓性格同我大仔有啲似 我諗2-3日就可以放出籠相處下<br />\n唔打大架就ok 如見到大貓比人恰 反擊唔到<br />\n適當時你要企出黎叫停細貓 要比細貓知 佢唔係大佬<br />\n同埋細貓會係咁叫係因為驚&gt;嬲 比啲耐性"},{"pid":"64e0c50c7e194e939db85e307613c40314500b64","tid":88752,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:54:27.000Z","msg":"急屎急尿"},{"pid":"59f4dd915c860646f225e5edd16f7b500b793b24","tid":88752,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓B一定係咁 當初我接我細女返黎都係<br />\n叫到我都好怕佢會啞 係幾日後就唔再嘈<br />\n你大貓性格同我大仔有啲似 我諗2-3日就可以放出籠相處下<br />\n唔打大架就ok 如見到大貓比人恰 反擊唔到<br />\n適當時你要企出黎叫停細貓 要比細貓知 佢唔係大佬<br />\n同埋細貓會係咁叫係因為驚&amp;gt;嬲 比啲耐性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果有多啲大貓+大仔性格嘅貓就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢家下唔單止嗌 仲會出爪亂爪 <br />\n我好驚佢會整損自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我岩岩望過下 佢眼仔紅哂 似係捱夜唔訓狂叫<img src=\"/assets